data.description: Don't miss this Mountain Meadows end unit, one level condo. Great floor plan that includes a large living room w/ gas insert fireplace.Features plenty of windows for natural afternoon light. Dining area leading to the kitchen.Two bed, two full baths. The first bedroom has access off of the entryway & features a storage closet along w/a regular closet. Catch the views out of the window to Mt. Ashland. Hallway bath has a tub/shower combo. Spacious storage closet off of the hallway that has built-ins along w/extra hanging storage. Large primary bedroom w/a bathroom that features a walk-in shower. One car garage w/extra storage as well. All this plus community amenities - clubhouse, dining room, wood shop, 4 acre park, community garden, fitness center w/indoor pool all at Ashland's only resort style 55+ community Mountain Meadows. There are 2 associations, Mt. Meadows owners monthly 780.87/1 & 1010.87/2. Hillside Condo Assoc. monthly dues $241.60 a month. Assumable VA Loan available.
